  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "intro_1",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Why did the police have to push Jumbo off the main street?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 11.07,
      "endTime": 17.77,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Last Christmas, the circus owner, Jimmy Gates, decided to take some presents to a children's hospital.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 17.78,
      "endTime": 26.84
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Dressed up as Father Christmas and accompanied by a 'guard of honour' of six pretty girls,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 26.85,
      "endTime": 33.99
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "he set off down the main street of the city riding a baby elephant called Jumbo.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 34,
      "endTime": 41.59
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "He should have known that the police would never allow this sort of thing.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 41.6,
      "endTime": 47.86,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "A policeman approached Jimmy and told him he ought to have gone along a side street as Jumbo was holding up the traffic.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 47.87,
      "endTime": 57.77,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Policeman",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "警察"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Though Jimmy agreed to go at once, Jumbo refused to move.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 57.78,
      "endTime": 64.86,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Fifteen policemen had to push very hard to get him off the main street.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 64.87,
      "endTime": 71.04,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Very",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "很，非常"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The police had a difficult time, but they were most amused.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 71.05,
      "endTime": 76.71
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "'Jumbo must weigh a few tons,' said a policeman afterwards,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 76.72,
      "endTime": 82.76,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Policeman",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "警察"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "'so it was fortunate that we didn't have to carry him.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 82.77,
      "endTime": 87.78,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Of course, we should arrest him, but as he has a good record, we shall let him off this time.'",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 87.79,
      "endTime": 92.79,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
